{"tid":166584,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人可以救救我？成日覺得做漏嘢/攞漏嘢咁，去到病態地步！","createTime":"2017-03-22T08:31:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T08:08:00.000Z","uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8c9c97d4b8d9bed567f4fef033816ad85bb97d96","tid":166584,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T08:31:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每次離開一個地區要check3-4次冇漏嘢<br />\n走個時都要回望多幾次，<br />\n走咗都仲會擔心多5分鐘<br />\n<br />\n而臨瞓就成日驚冇扭實水龍頭<br />\n要扭足五次先安樂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如此類推<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開始覺得自己有啲病態<br />\n忍唔到要咁做<br />\n但唔做又唔得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇方法解決/醫治？"},{"pid":"7e0de94a745f3cd143a76cc33b76df8bb548cc96","tid":166584,"uid":92535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T08:32:24.000Z","msg":"係咪焦慮症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a42aad144d90aeb0c0576248b468530e263c72","tid":166584,"uid":22949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T08:36:13.000Z","msg":"代表你夠鐘食藥lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f3b3ad5c122986a71d2b397b3dee0723b84d98","tid":166584,"uid":1928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T08:38:13.000Z","msg":"係有病 要睇醫生"},{"pid":"a1385cb8944c87e0a76d6f5817fe8685b812ab5d","tid":166584,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T08:38:42.000Z","msg":"97後，成日覺得自己後面個袋俾人打開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac0b94a71f668cf5a5786d01e3eb62a6b7e7172",