/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊到求症？</blockquote><br />\n搵下啲私家 有精神科都睇得<br />\n留個tg:iamnotcare <br />\n有問題可以問我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最緊要幫到你</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係啵， 我係<span style=\"color: red;\">醫管局員工家屬</span><br />\n我應該可以直接去職員診所睇睇等佢轉介？</blockquote><br />\n因為一般睇政府排好耐 所以唔太建議 <br />\n除非覺得自己唔太嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw家屬可以打尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nNo <br />\n我排皮膚科都係要等兩年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔識定義嚴唔嚴重<br />\n我就覺得驚漏嘢呢個情況已經到病態<br />\n好影響到我自己<br />\n但睇完其他病症，又唔覺自己係嚴重個堆<br />\n因為生理上好似冇乜影響，應該叫正常嘅"},{"pid":"f9c89e43df62531867c72f27a5ffacf5d8e94ade","tid":166584,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:01:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尋晚扭水龍頭<br />\n搞咗十次<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要係隻手啱啱離開就忍唔住要再扭"},{"pid":"5e67baf2941c95e776b4a8d1a2da7c61cc0b88c9","tid":166584,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:03:07.000Z","msg":"自制check list"},{"pid":"15587c09f54abbd81fcdb73d1697dd1339618d49","tid":166584,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:05:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自制check list</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 問題係check list每一項要check十幾次<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇有冇攞漏嘢<br />\n明明得藥，筆袋，書，筆記，耳機<br />\n都要點完再點<br />\n點足5次先可以勉強停"},{"pid":"c12a18344150bb47553a88b3706c9348edd8f2d9","tid":166584,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:06:26.000Z","msg":"你係咪癡線架...."},{"pid":"35f05a10bf3489753c1798db48728b243e7f5e72","tid":166584,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":